data.description: Enjoy rural living in the heart of quaint Cornville, just off Page Springs Road! This 3 br/2 ba 1561 sqft home not only comes with all appliances included but is conveniently and centrally located a mere matter of minutes away from local wineries, social eateries and services throughout the Verde Valley! Take pleasure in the privacy of this fully fenced property, tucked away from the main road and speckled with beautiful Mesquite trees. With plenty of outdoor storage and a detached garage/workshop, you will have more than enough space to store all of your tools and toys! Bring your chickens, goats, and storage totes and make yourself at home!
